data.description: Brand new, elegant, custom home ready for Immediate occupancy! Located in the new development of First Tenth, this home is only one of 15 lots, and is right off of Route 10 in the Caesar Rodney School District. Start your tour of the home with the hardwood foyer, angled staircase, 9 ft ceilings throughout the first floor, and admire the arched door ways and bull nose corners throughout the home. Gourmet kitchen with custom built cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting and ceramic tile; open living room with custom windows, formal dining room with bay window, crown and chair molding. Spacious master suite with a large walk-in closet & full bath featuring ceramic tile & soaker tub. Come see this beautiful home built by Elite Homes while it is still available. Other lots and floor plans are available by request. Owner will consider lease-purchase. For more information, call our 24 hour Real Estate Hotline:  888-613-6486, then enter code 6710 or visit our website at www.firstclassproperties.us and enter MLS #5058431.  For a tour of this home call 302 677 0770.
